name: A E S T H E T I C Webpage Generator
tagline: A web generator made in Python.
body:
# A E S T H E T I C Webpage Generator

## Creates random webpages using Python and the Giphy API.

### Created and Maintained by:
- [Downtown Development] (https://github.com/DowntownDevelopment)

Last Updated: 08/31/2016

### Requirements
- Python 3+
- pip
- A rebellious attitude

### Installation
1. download zip or clone repo
2. run `pip install -r requirements.txt`
3. open index.html in your favorite browser (internet explorer 6)
4. google pictures of cute kittens to unsee what you have seen.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
